des: We recognize that the heart of Christian Country music speaks to the abundant love God desires for His children to experience. Our vision is to be a vessel of that love by playing music from broken people who have found that love not only to be true, but necessary. We recognize we all need to walk in accordance to scripture and to love the Lord with all our heart, mind, and strength and, to love one another.
